<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="listen-vi">listen <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lɪsn/    美 /'lɪsn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>听：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He listened but heard nothing. 
他听了听，但什么也没听见。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>listened to</strong> him play / playing a piece of music. 
我听他弹了一首曲子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>听信；听从：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She refused to <strong>listen to</strong> my advice. 
她不肯听我的劝告。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[口语] 听着；听好</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="listen-for">listen for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>留神等着听</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="listen-in">listen in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>收听 (电台的广播)</strong>  </p>
<p>2.★ <strong>偷听；窃听 (on)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Never read other people's mails or <strong>listen in on</strong> personal conversations.
不要读他人的信件或偷听私人谈话。</p><footer>2009 全国改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>listener /'lɪsənə(r)/ n [C]  </p>
<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>We were invited to attend a private concert, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(listen) to musicians and meeting interesting locals.  （2019全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. listening  </p></div>